## Auth Flow Diagram

```mermaid
graph TD
    A[Login Page] --> B{Method?}
    B -->|Username + Password| C[CredentialsProvider]
    B -->|Google Button| D[GoogleProvider]
    C --> E[Check DB: username match?]
    E -->|Yes + password match| F[Return user token]
    E -->|No| G[Error: Invalid credentials]
    D --> H[Google OAuth consent]
    H --> I[signIn callback]
    I --> J{User exists by email?}
    J -->|Yes| K[Use existing user]
    J -->|No| L[Auto-create student user]
    K --> F
    L --> F
    F --> M[JWT + Session]
    M --> N[Role-based redirect]
```

